snippet.title: The Axis Unseen - Official Gameplay Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2024
snippet.description: Check out gameplay and see bizarre monsters in this new The Axis Unseen trailer for the upcoming heavy metal horror game. The Axis Unseen will be available on PC in October 2024. The Axis Unseen is a heavy metal horror game created by one of the developers of Skyrim, Starfield and Fallout. Hunt nightmarish monsters from ancient folklore in a mysterious open world, collecting their enhanced sense powers and discovering elemental arrows. Beware, the hunter is also the hunted.
